106
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,000
Dia cuma

107
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,120
memburukkan keadaan?

108
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,399
Cepat halau dia!

109
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,519
Halau dia?

110
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:23,600
Dia pemimpin sekte.

111
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,480
Aku tak berani halau sesuka hati.

112
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,800
Kenapa Cik Chu duduk
di tempat utama?

113
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,560
Hari ini hari jadi Chang.

114
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,759
Mestilah dia duduk di tempat kehormat.

115
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,839
Tepat.

116
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,160
Rong,

117
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:47,040
kita tetamu di sini.

118
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,120
Jangan membebel.

119
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,160
Bagi pihak Sekte Tiga Tangan,

120
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:58,680
saya ucapkan Selamat Hari Jadi ke-20, Cik Chu!

121
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,079
Tak perlu begitu.

122
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:03,120
Lagipun, awak kawan mak cik dan pak cik saya.

123
00:05:05,399 --> 00:05:06,160
Cik Chu,

124
00:05:06,399 --> 00:05:08,920
sila terima baju bertatah mutiara ini sebagai hadiah.

125
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,720
Baju mutiara?

126
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,639
Saya ingat Puteri Gaochang pernah ada satu,

127
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,279
yang dilapor dicuri baru-baru ini.

128
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,160
Er...

129
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:17,240
Kebetulan sungguh.

130
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:18,959
Tengok pada kilauannya,

131
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,680
ini pasti tiruan, kan?

132
00:05:21,639 --> 00:05:22,480
Ya, ya!

133
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,040
Betul.

134
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,480
Kalau Cik Chu tak berkenan itu,

135
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:27,560
saya juga ada Tongkat Jed ini.

136
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,120
Barang ini

137
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:31,399
diambil dari Makam Putera Qin...

138
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:38,560
maksud saya, dibeli dari kedai antik tepi makam itu.

139
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,480
Dengan hadiah semewah ini,

140
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:44,519
berapa banyak duit kau terhutang pada keluarga itu?

141
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,560
Terima kasih.

142
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,360
Zhizhi,

143
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:51,040
bawa tuan ini ke balai sisi untuk minum teh.

144
00:05:52,279 --> 00:05:53,160
Silakan ikut sini.

145
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:56,170
- Silakan dulu.
- Jom.

146
00:06:00,225 --> 00:06:01,785
(Kediaman Chu) Saya dah cukup berlakon.

147
00:06:01,785 --> 00:06:03,904
Dah sampai masa kamu beritahu kami kebenaran.

148
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,800
Kebenaran apa?

149
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,000
Sebenarnya keluarga Mao buat kerja apa?

150
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,260
Mereka berkhidmat untuk Kementerian Hasil.

151
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:11,040
Kementerian Hasil?

152
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,160
Kau ingat kami ni bodoh?

153
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,279
Dengan sikap mereka yang biadab dan angkuh itu?

154
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,959
Bagi saya, bukan macam itu.

155
00:06:17,170 --> 00:06:18,480
Lebih macam Kementerian Kehakiman.

156
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,480
Mak cik...

157
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:23,279
Tengok Mao Buyu itu.

158
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,800
Pada kamu, dia nampak bijak?

159
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,600
Masih tak nak beritahu kebenaran?

160
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,680
Baik.

161
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,959
Tapi bila nanti kau terkena padah,

162
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,720
jangan datang mengadu pada kami.

163
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,240
Chang,

164
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,439
mak cik kamu betul.

165
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:35,350
Keluarga kita dalam keadaan serba salah.

166
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:37,120
Jangan main api.

167
00:06:38,612 --> 00:06:39,331
Cik,

168
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:40,639
Li Wan datang lagi.

169
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,800
Salam, Ketua Sekte Chu.

170
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,839
Kenapa kamu balik secepat ini?

171
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,920
Ketua Sekte, sesuatu besar dah berlaku.

172
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,839
Ratu Pencuri dari Selatan sudah tiba.

173
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,199
Dia dah hapuskan Geng Harimau Hitam.

174
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,360
Dia menuntut

175
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:57,120
supaya kita semua tunduk padanya.

176
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,319
Dia beri amaran, kalau kami tak ikut,

177
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,120
sekte kami akan dimusnahkan selepas ini.

178
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:04,279
Sejak Sekte Tangan Suci hilang Token Suci,

179
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,839
kita tak sekuat dulu.

180
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:09,040
Tapi kita masih pemimpin Persekutuan Persilatan.

181
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,279
Siapa perempuan ini?

182
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,040
Macam mana dia boleh begitu angkuh?

183
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,639
Er...

184
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,560
Persekutuan dan pencuri Selatan

185
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:18,720
dari dulu kekal di wilayah masing-masing.

186
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,240
Perempuan ini terang-terangan melanggar batas.

187
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:24,160
Ketua Sekte Chu, tolong bela pihak kami!

188
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:27,160
Saya takkan campur tangan.

189
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,519
Apa?

190
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,759
Cari bantuan di tempat lain.

191
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:32,519
Apa?!

192
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,720
Ketua Sekte! Ketua Sekte!

193
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,800
Ketua Sekte!

194
00:07:37,399 --> 00:07:38,040
Para Pengawal,

195
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,879
apa yang dia fikirkan?

196
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,000
Kita di bawah Persekutuan Persilatan!

197
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,759
Musuh sedang menyerang kita,

198
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:46,240
dan dia terus beredar begitu saja?

199
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:49,160
Dia nak tengok kita semua lenyap?

200
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,800
Dia ada sebabnya.

201
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,839
Ada yang tak kena dengan keluarga Chu.

202
00:07:58,040 --> 00:08:00,439
Takkan kamu tak rasa perangai mereka hari ini

203
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:03,040
buktikan mereka sembunyikan sesuatu daripada kita?

204
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,000
Semua orang ada rahsia.

205
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,959
Lagipun, kita belum cukup rapat

206
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:07,680
untuk mereka beritahu kita

207
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,720
setiap butiran

208
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,680
tentang hidup mereka.

209
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,040
Buyu,

210
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,879
lelaki yang datang memberi hormat itu memang mencurigakan.

211
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:17,240
Dia langsung tak nampak macam saudagar.

212
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,959
Dia nampak macam orang dunia persilatan.

213
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,160
Ayah betul.

214
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,399
Saya rasa Li Wan itu

215
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,120
ialah ketua Sekte Tiga Tangan

216
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,279
dalam fail Kor Risikan saya.

217
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,279
Kakak,

218
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,439
kita perlukan bukti sebelum bercakap.

219
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,800
Buyu,

220
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,000
keluarga mereka jelas ada masalah.

221
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,960
Tentang perkahwinan ini...

222
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,559
Kau perlu fikir masak-masak.

223
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,200
Ayah,

224
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,759
Chang memang untuk saya.

225
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,000
Saya hanya akan kahwini dia.

226
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,120
Saya takkan ubah fikiran.

227
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,120
Kenapa degil sangat?

228
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,440
Adakah Chu Yunchang benar-benar

229
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:47,320
satu-satunya wanita yang tinggal di dunia ini?

230
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,200
Ya, memang dia.

231
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,879
Kau nak abang kau

232
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,159
jadi orang bermuka-muka?

233
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,360
Perkahwinan kau mungkin sengsara,

234
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,639
tapi jangan cuba rosakkan perkahwinan aku.

235
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,920
Kau melampau!

236
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,440
Rong!

237
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,320
Macam mana kau boleh cakap begitu dengan kakak kau?

238
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:03,919
Lagipun,

239
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:05,559
dia dan suaminya memang sehaluan.

240
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,639
Mana ada mereka tak bahagia?

241
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:08,080
Mana ada mereka sengsara?

242
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:09,679
Rong!

243
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,159
Chang.

244
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:19,919
Makcik.

245
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,590
Sekte Tangan Suci memimpin
Pakatan Persilatan.

246
00:09:21,679 --> 00:09:23,039
Sebagai pemimpin sekte kita,

247
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,799
macam mana Makcik boleh abaikan

248
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:26,200
hakikat kita dibuli?

249
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,679
Lagipun, pencuri wanita itu mungkin datang

250
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:30,399
sebab

251
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:31,559
Tupai Jed.

252
00:09:33,279 --> 00:09:35,240
Itu buktikan rancangan aku menjadi.

253
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,559
Kita pancing Empat Pencuri Agung

254
00:09:37,679 --> 00:09:38,799
dan dapatkan semula Token Suci.

255
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:41,120
Sekte Tiga Tangan tak berbaloi

256
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,080
untuk kita lindungi.

257
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,399
Apa yang kau merepek?

258
00:09:44,879 --> 00:09:48,240
Tiga bulan lepas,
empangan di Daerah Tong runtuh.

259
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,399
Entah berapa keluarga terpaksa berpindah,

260
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,000
dan ribuan maut.

261
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,080
Makcik,

262
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,559
Makcik tahu semua itu.

263
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:57,320
Tapi apa kena-mengena dengan ini?

264
00:09:57,559 --> 00:09:58,559
Daripada apa yang aku siasat,

265
00:09:58,559 --> 00:10:01,120
Sekte Tiga Tangan
langgar peraturan pakatan kita.

266
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,880
Mereka curi bekalan bantuan bencana,

267
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,679
buat mangsa
langsung tak ada apa-apa.

268
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,000
Tak boleh diterima!

269
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,240
Sanggup buat kerja sekejam itu...

270
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,440
Langgar peraturan pakatan,

271
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,799
buat jahat macam itu,

272
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,440
dan sakiti orang tak bersalah,

273
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,440
mereka patut dihapuskan!

274
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,279
Sepatutnya beritahu aku dari awal.

275
00:10:18,279 --> 00:10:19,970
Aku sendiri
dah ajar mereka satu pengajaran.

276
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,290
Tak perlu beri amaran pada mereka.

277
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,639
Aku sebenarnya nak pencuri wanita itu

278
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,279
muncul cepat.

279
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,120
Menyampah betul!

280
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,200
Kalau Sekte Tangan Suci
tak berpeluk tubuh,

281
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,759
Geng Harimau Hitam dan Naga Hijau
takkan tumbang.

282
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:34,679
Baik.

283
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:38,879
Kalau masa genting pun mereka tak bantu,

284
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,559
kita saja yang menyerah.

285
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:45,799
Tapi kalau buat begitu,

286
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:47,679
memalukan sangat.

287
00:10:48,025 --> 00:10:50,080
Kita kena bagi hadiah besar pada mereka.

288
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:51,520
Hadiah apa?

289
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:55,812
Guru Agung Pakatan Persilatan,
Chu Yunchang.

290
00:10:59,679 --> 00:11:00,799
Sudi datang lagi!

291
00:11:00,799 --> 00:11:01,639
Cik Mao.

292
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,679
Sekarang cuma saya seorang di kedai.

293
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,799
Bagus. Aku datang cari kau.

294
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,360
Aku?

295
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,200
Aku cuma tahu siram bunga,

296
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,600
yang lain tak tahu.

297
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,559
Aku tak percaya.

298
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,320
Kau bukan sekadar tanam bunga.

299
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,559
Kau bela serangga juga.

300
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:20,159
Serangga berbisa untuk racun, kan?

301
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:21,750
Serangga berbisa?

302
00:11:21,962 --> 00:11:24,523
Kami penjual bunga paling benci serangga.

303
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:26,440
Jangan sebarkan khabar angin begitu.

304
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,600
Baik. Aku beli pokok.

305
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,759
Kau nak pokok?

306
00:11:29,759 --> 00:11:31,919
Kami ada banyak spesies
yang jarang dan eksotik.

307
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:33,240
Kau cari yang macam mana?

308
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,200
Aku tunjukkan sekeliling.

309
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,080
Tak perlu. Aku pilih sendiri.

310
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,200
Cik Mao...

311
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:40,120
Cik Mao!

312
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,519
Belakang rumah tak boleh masuk!

313
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,200
Nampak tak?

314
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:48,240
Aku belum sempat habiskan amaran pun.

315
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:53,240
Cik Mao, aku memang kagum.

316
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,159
Sepanjang hidup aku,

317
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:57,000
itu kali pertama aku nampak orang
tumbuk sarang lebah dengan tangan kosong.

318
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,399
Kau dah tipu aku!

319
00:11:58,679 --> 00:11:59,679
Aku tak!

320
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,960
Aku cuba halang, tapi tak sempat!

321
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:04,519
Tengok tu!

322
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:06,679
Muka dia bengkak macam bantal!

323
00:12:07,679 --> 00:12:09,159
Zhizhi, kau kenapa?

324
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,200
Rong,

325
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,960
aku ada salap herba yang terbaik.

326
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,039
Memang sesuai untuk gigitan serangga.

327
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:16,960
Nah.

328
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,080
Padan muka dia.

329
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,440
Rong, kau datang sini

330
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:27,679
ada tujuan tertentu?

331
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,100
Aku tanya terus terang.

332
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,559
Siapa sebenarnya lelaki itu

333
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:35,039
yang jumpa kau masa hari jadi kau?

334
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,440
Dah aku cakap, kan?

335
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,720
Dia kawan pak cik aku.

336
00:12:40,759 --> 00:12:42,480
Aku tak percaya, Chu Yunchang.

337
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,080
Jangan ingat kau dah padam jejak.

338
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,240
Aku bukan orang yang boleh dipermain.

339
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,919
Aku akan cari bukti jenayah kau.

340
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,519
Mesti ada salah faham.

341
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,240
(Lelaki hari itu)

342
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,790
(mesti Li Wan,
pemimpin Sekte Tiga Tangan.)

343
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:05,440
(Apa hubungan sebenar dia
dengan Chu Yunchang?)

344
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,000
Cik, nak beli pemerah pipi?

345
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,799
Bagus untuk kulit cik.

346
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:09,480
Jangan kacau aku!

347
00:13:10,399 --> 00:13:11,639
Apa masalah kau?

348
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,639
Chu Yunchang...

349
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,879
Aku belum selesai dengan kau!

350
00:13:19,450 --> 00:13:22,725
♪Dendam dan sesal
bagai arak yang keras♪

351
00:13:22,775 --> 00:13:25,650
♪Teguk saja, kemudian lepaskan♪

352
00:13:25,925 --> 00:13:31,643
♪Cawan kosong untuk cinta dan benci♪

353
00:13:33,123 --> 00:13:36,443
♪Air mata mengaburkan takdir yang tak mampu aku kawal♪

354
00:13:36,443 --> 00:13:39,363
♪Mari minum sampai subuh♪

355
00:13:40,250 --> 00:13:45,490
♪Di sebalik topeng ini, aku takkan berdusta♪

356
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:49,443
♪Setiap pertemuan semula terasa seperti pertama kali♪

357
00:13:49,443 --> 00:13:53,093
♪Senyum tersembunyi ini takkan pudar♪

358
00:13:53,163 --> 00:13:56,653
♪Satu hati, tetap di sisi mu♪

359
00:13:56,863 --> 00:13:59,838
♪Hingga ke hujung waktu♪

360
00:13:59,888 --> 00:14:03,125
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

361
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:06,925
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

362
00:14:06,975 --> 00:14:13,215
♪Untuk mencari mu
dan menepati janji kita selamanya♪

363
00:14:13,388 --> 00:14:16,603
♪Doa sunyi dalam jiwaku♪

364
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:20,438
♪Mendukung sumpahku di bawah bulan♪

365
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:23,775
♪Berharap kita takkan terpisah lagi♪

366
00:14:23,775 --> 00:14:26,875
♪Dalam perjalanan menuju selamanya♪

367
00:14:26,913 --> 00:14:30,763
♪Bulan melakar wajahmu♪

368
00:14:30,763 --> 00:14:34,123
♪Diselimuti awan, kau penuhi hatiku♪

369
00:14:34,483 --> 00:14:40,443
♪Untuk mencari mu
dan menepati janji kita selamanya♪

370
00:14:41,363 --> 00:14:51,003
♪Hanya untuk bersama mu♪

